snippet.title: Luminary Gameplay Trailer | 2021
snippet.description:
Join our Discord server for them gaimz: https://discord.gg/jVVdzjHDAX

Luminary takes the Openworld RPG, and dials it in for a balanced accessible experience, with a procedural twist. Using a unique world level and character proficiency system, explore the vast lands together, uncover hidden treasures, defeat large scale bosses, and rid the world’s darkness with light.
